# Paths excluded from renv's dependency discovery (same syntax as .gitignore).
# These are archived / legacy instructor materials. They still contain
# library() calls (e.g. library(rdd)) for packages we do not want re-added to
# renv.lock when running renv::snapshot(). Excluding them keeps the lockfile
# scoped to the current course code.
OLD/
Tom_Slides/
Tom_2023_Slides/
